Interface WSDLExtensionLoader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddressingWSDLExtensionLoader, HTTPWSDLExtensionLoader, JMSWSDLExtensionLoader, WSDLExtensionRegister, XMLWSDLExtensionLoader

    public interface WSDLExtensionLoader
    Marker interface to mark beans in the config that register addition WSDLExtensors so the WSDLManager can load the additional extensors on demand
